text:
We'd like to extend a huge thanks for our
100,000th view on our YouTube channel.

We're blown away by the support and we've
got more to do.

We originally started making videos about
Korea but now we're traveling around SE Asia,

so thanks for sticking around and next up
it is Cambodia.

We've got a lot to show you there from temples
to beaches to whatever.

Please stick around and we'll have a lot more
to come.
